Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government will be \Naddressing the nation shortly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make an important announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave your TV on and stand \Nby without changing the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you know, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are both a bit clueless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and both have a bit of the \Nwrong idea about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but they share the immensely strong, loving \Nbond between servant and mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! And you just start the opening \Nlike there's nothing going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what's this important announcement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:54.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:03.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:08.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:13.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:18.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:24.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naïve and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:40.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:08.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Amuro May Have Had a \NPlace to Return to, But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? M-Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have chosen my words carefully, Persian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But you did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you don't have to work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is Sparta's answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is blasphemy! Madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, what are you looking so down for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that to say that you're firing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You barely managed to pass that \Ntest the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail the upcoming finals, \Nyou'll seriously be on thin ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm saying you can take a \Nbreak from your butler duties
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and focus on your studies \Nuntil the exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can handle that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't show such concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall we say that you'll get \Nfired if your grades are bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not graciously accept her offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a great kindness that your \Nmistress is showing you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just study hard without \Nstraining yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to play hard with \Nme once the tests are over,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so brace yourself. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I got smacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel a bit apprehensive, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus is currently out \Nand absent as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, what are you saying, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a butler in \Nconstant attendance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say, but who's the one who \Ngot into a desperate situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to be barely saved when \Nyou had no butler with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a coincidence! A coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In preparation for just such an event...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives, Klaus? That was a \Nwaste of a perfectly good TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In preparation for just such a \Nsituation, I made some arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrangements?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a new temporary butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you certain you're \Nfine with keeping me company?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ya sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer workin' hard for Nagi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's my duty as the \Npartner to help ya out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer not makin' any progress here! \NWhat're ya spacin' out for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right for me to \Nbe taking time off work to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for that, looks like ya \Ngot nothin' to worry 'bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard somethin' 'bout a new butler comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new... butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I overheard the SP guys \Nsayin' somethin' like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea! I see! I \Nsee! That's news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Does that upset ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not letting it upset me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she really hates strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I imagine anyone who isn't me \Nwill have a hard time with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But while yer sittin' here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and the new butler might \Nbecome friendly and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see nothing wrong with \Nthem becoming friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. It's time to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Newest Edition\NBasic Problem Collection\NComprehensive English
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to live up to the faith \Nthe Miss has placed in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, "atarashii shitsuji"... "New butler".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A new butler come soon"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coming soon dead"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon now, don't slip in ominous \Nsoundin' phrases into yer English.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it bothers ya that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't ya peek in on 'em on yer \Nway to the bathroom or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't see the need \Nto get so upset 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Himegami told ya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's countin' on ya \Nto take care of Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have confidence. Yer the only \Nbutler that suits Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ya think ya could put more \Nfaith in the bond ya have with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bond with the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for losing my composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it. C'mon, let's \Nget focused, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go to the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pull myself together \Nbefore I resume my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}So in the end, he's still upset. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! Like hell I need a new butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never accept another \Nbutler, who is not Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this butler is extremely capable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I believe there is no doubt that \Nhe will be of more use than Ayasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to breathe the same \Nair as a butler that's not Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are certain to come \Nto like me, Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure to meet you. I \Nam Mecha Butler No. 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Send him \Nback to Miss Makimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, Miss Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is basically what \Nthey were referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? This is borin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can relax and \Ndevote myself to my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study hard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}But this was where Hayate's \Nguard was not up! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responding in some way is the \Npolite thing to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does its words actually count \Nas an expression of gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a manga drawn by you, Miss Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Where do you get off looking \Nat it without my permission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your butt out of her already, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lousy manga it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if a robot like you could understand \Nthe greatness of my manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the characters do have impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The layout and dialogue also have \Na certain sensibility to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The art isn't bad, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the plot developments are abrupt, \Nwhich overshadow the good parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to think about your reader more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You are smart, so your level of \Ncomprehension is higher than average.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your readers will be seeing it for \Nthe first time, so that won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you read that manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't reach it, so I haven't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please read it, because it \Nwill serve as a good reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an extremely fine piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try reading it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rose tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soothe you and allow \Nyou to read at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you have time to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Mecha Butler, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the path of Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and by overclocking, I can move \Nmore swiftly than human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, Miss Maria, I would like \Nto help with the cleaning and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? O-Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us start over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please don't move. It seems \Nyour shoulders are a bit stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, a-all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be capable of doing \Neverything on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but working too hard can be a problem, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}But he's really good at this. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}I think I might kind of like it... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, No. 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll just instruct me, I'll \Ndo the rest of the work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the foolish desire of a guy to \Nact cool in front of a cute girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please, let me act cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not doing any butler work at all \Nmakes me feel restless somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I wonder \Nif that robot butler's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, you're quite good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to win the next round!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not go so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Wh-What in the world is this? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Somehow... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}...he's completely fitting in now. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Long ago, there was an episode of "Doraemon" {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}where a guy's shadow took the guy's place. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so ominous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Small Light.\N({\u1}Su{\u0}-Su-Su-Sumouru rai{\u1}to{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-M-M-M-My existence has finally become...\N({\u1}To{\u0}-To-To-To-To-Toutou boku no sonzai {\u1}ga{\u0}...)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hayate's getting jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks like the way you've \Nbecome friendly with that robot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is really gettin' to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a butler robot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The technology of the Sanzenin \Nfamily sure is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored to receive \Nyour words of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how outstandin' are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm askin' ya, ya moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made a jab at him without even meanin' to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reputation precedes you, Miss Sakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not overlook even \Nthe smallest of jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya mean, that was on purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Outstandin'! This Robot Butler's \Nso outstandin', it's mind-blowin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's getting jealous over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, he's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss, why do you look so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, to think Hayate \Nwould get jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit endearing, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There ya go with yer warped \Nsensibilities again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an emotion that is \Nenjoyable for human beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are there things even \Nyou don't understand, No. 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because my CPU hasn't been \Nprogrammed with thought patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that encourage negative \Nemotions in human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine that you're \Nnot programmed with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is correct, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I got everything right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Somehow, being a bit depressed \Nactually makes me more focused. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Human beings are strange creatures. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely a gloom \Nabout him from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what jealousy \Nlooks like. I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit grinnin' like a fool and \Ngo on in to comfort him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he should be getting \Ntired from his studies soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe I'll make him \Nsome tea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, No. 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to comfort him right away, \Nyou'll be playing right into his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. The adult gambit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so this is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, H-Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made some tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you going to the \Ntrouble of making me tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, please think nothing of it, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are your studies going well, meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Honestly! What about this \Nis a good idea, No. 13?! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Hayate doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staring all goggly at Maria like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's not bein' all goggly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will be taking some time off, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Hayate! How dare you look \Nat Maria with those pervy eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, but it seems \Nthis plan has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}And with that, I've gotten rid of person #1. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us take this in a slightly \Ndifferent direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! A late night snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not night yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll pull out all the stops to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to make a loving dish here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously leadin' to the totally \Ncliche explosion punch line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya can't even fix up a single \Nservin' of cup ramen properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would not mind, would you \Nlend a hand as well, Miss Sakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made all of this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Eat up and work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you were a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, this stuff is nothin' extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing, being encouraged by Saku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that person named Hayate is \Nquite close to Miss Sakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate is... Hayate is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, this food is so comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be getting comforted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Hayate, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss, what are you so angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be in a foul mood, so \Nperhaps you should take your leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? She's such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sakuya, you are more \Nmature than Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya sure are a smooth talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be goin' then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Now, that makes two. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}That just leaves... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, are you getting \Nanywhere with your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've gotten quite a bit done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and I owe it to Sakuya for \Nreally drumming it into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about owing to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you owe it more to Saku than to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, Miss, th-that is not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! I swear, Hayate is just so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he is quite a poor butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he seems to be awfully stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, wouldn't he be considered \Na failure as a Sanzenin butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 13, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, don't you think \NI should just remain your butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us forget about someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am superior to him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pitiful. Getting so depressed \Nover something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. When I think of what \Nwould be good for you, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, that's not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with me by your side, your picky \Neating habits never get any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you keep watching TV late into the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you skip school and play \Nnothing but online games,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lately, you've gained \Nan interest in Otome Road
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you've been secretly sending \NSP members shopping there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, behind the shelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and only you are my butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You being a bit less than outstanding \Nis a better fit for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, does that count as a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, w-well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, right now, just study hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Could it be that he behaved \Nlike that for my sake? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a bit less than \Noutstanding is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings are so complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eight! Stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to lose you to him, I'd \Nrather wreck him and go down with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go down with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Eight, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hurt at all, No. 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was he angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had done no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I kept focusing \Nall my attention on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it looks like he got jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous? I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That emotion has not been \Nprogrammed into me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine. I don't \Nreally understand it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one isn't as high-performance \Nas you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't understand, no matter \Nhow high-performance I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My being at this residence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ultimately serves as a hindrance \Nto Miss Nagi's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave the rest to \NHayate and I will just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking news!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! What is it?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant meteor that has suddenly \Ncome flying out of space
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is currently approaching Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears it will land in Tokyo's \NNerima Ward in just a few minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's already right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or actually, so the scene before \Nthe opening really had meaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it's gonna hit us head-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hurry and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, at that size, you will \Nnot be able to flee in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, please take care of \Nthe Miss and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy the meteor in space, \Nbefore it damages the Earth's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use the self-destruct \Nmechanism built into me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it should be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer gonna self-destruct?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go! No. 13, this is \Nan order from your mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it is a butler's duty \Nto protect his mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it costs him his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me for disobeying your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! I'm never letting you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, No. 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, please get the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Miss, get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am ever given the opportunity \Nto be reborn again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be sure to have the emotion of \Njealousy programmed into me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure was a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}No. 13... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant meteor that came \Nflying out of space yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow vanished just before \Nit collided with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Thanks to the Mecha Butler \NNo. 13's courageous deed, {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}peace on Earth and the happiness of \Nthe Sanzenin Miss were protected. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Thank you, No. 13. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Farewell, Mecha Butler No. 13. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:05.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:10.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:14.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:22.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:32.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:41.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:47.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:56.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn, marble soul! I'm Nagi Sanzenin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, this is your character song, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deluge of "Hayate the Combat \NButler" character songs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has tapered off, so they decided \Nthey could play my song again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure the next song \Njust didn't get done in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. Though, it's true \Nthat it hasn't been sung yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so anyway, we're prepared \Na fan service shot of Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross-dressing Hayate is nice, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for all the Hayate \Nfans across the nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this time, we have a pinup of \NHayate in his butler uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get a picture \Nof me like this, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is better than the cross-dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:23:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:58.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:18.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:23:59.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:01.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter that's not signed by the sender?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:05.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's got quite a lot of \Nnerve to send me a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:06.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But who in the world could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:07.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:08.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:09.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:11.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So is this letter from you, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:13.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Hina Love".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 48 is a must-see \Nepisode for Hinagiku fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:17.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I won't be appearing in it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:21.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Come Izen-cross with "Hayate the \NCombat Butler" again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina Love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.43,0:24:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
